---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Directory Data Enrichment Service | Stackbase System" description="Optional data enrichment service for directory projects: structured fields, normalization, and import-ready quality control.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="text-sm text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-wider">DATA ENRICHMENT</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-5 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Directory data enrichment service (optional, transparent, scoped)</h1>
      <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg max-w-3xl">Your directory is only as strong as its data quality. Stackbase offers optional enrichment for teams that need structured listing data, consistent formatting, and cleaner imports without hidden bundling tactics.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-2">Basic enrichment</h2>
        <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] mb-4">$0.50 / listing</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• Name, location, website, phone</li><li>• Category and field normalization</li><li>• Import-ready formatting and mapping</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-2">Premium enrichment</h2>
        <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] mb-4">$1.00 / listing</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• Everything in basic package</li><li>• Deeper attributes and listing descriptions</li><li>• QA pass before final import</li></ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">How we keep it trustworthy</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-[#c7c7d2]"><p>• Enrichment is optional, never forced inside core build plans</p><p>• BYOD imports are supported if you already own your data</p><p>• Scope is priced clearly per listing, not vague retainers</p><p>• Final output is structured for clean ingestion and QA</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f0ff] to-[#00c8ff] rounded-xl">See all add-ons</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">Request enrichment quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
